Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 差不多来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 每日锻炼结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没和你来一局了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开店前的准备做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要继承家业的话 也是时候记得过来帮把手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说要继承家业了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有好多事情想要做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H大业？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 我有叫你来帮忙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你拿着吃饭的家伙做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是有两个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}昨夜7时左右 在涩谷区的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}发生了住在该区内的45岁的资产家遇袭事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这种事情很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇袭的都是有钱人吧？ 和咱们家无关嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 如果你被卷入这类事件的话你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办啊？ 被盯上的都是有钱人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了是「如果」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车到山前必有路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老爸的话会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗？ 船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真像是有两个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要迟到？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 禁止骑摩托上学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次老师还训斥了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是骑去学校附近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算是回答吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他到底像谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说几次了 你拿着吃饭的家伙干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我最后一次看到老爸与妈妈的样子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.99,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1500)\pos(696,365)\4a&Hff&}马车与公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.99,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1500)\pos(696,365)\blur1}马车与公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近两个月 我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去一心先生那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他现在才自报身份出现在我面前？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生资产家遇袭事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么办？ 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 只要有我阿尔弗雷德在就无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能松开缰绳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是上品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人问你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下 我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧？ 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么 手无寸铁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑简单的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家爷爷 那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 可能会有点粗暴 请进车内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 赶快干掉那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 不能对你们客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 先要解决你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不了了 恶徒们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下死定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头 你大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没能保护好大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿尔弗雷德已经没有活着的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就送你去另一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要先清算这笔帐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对海瑟琳克家出手的罪孽之深 好好感受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂密的树叶成了缓冲垫 所以得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有个缓冲垫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:09:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「晚上好」的话有点太早了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿？ 为什么我会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你什么都不记得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走山路时的记忆我倒是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的 我叫夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特‧海瑟琳克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要开这种玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小林哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特‧海瑟…琳克？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像公主的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为我就是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要开这种玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种事情不是很习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于摸入睡女孩的胸部却习以为常？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧 对 偶然间碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我相信哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是都记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是和胸部事件扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂什么扯平了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 男生果然都喜欢大胸部的女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 因人而异…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩托车坏掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 没想像中的严重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和陌生男人在一起的话 会被训斥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那还真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来马车还真有点那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 得回去取行李才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢让我有马一心等他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我女儿‧佳苗的儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 是有马一心叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人我见多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背着的是刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话报警 有人违反刀枪管理法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我解释啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人是我重要的客人 不得怠慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一心老爷的客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 一心先生 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫我「外公」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时之间有点不适应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「爷爷」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说老爸与妈妈不是意外身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到仇人之后你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就轮到别人来找你寻仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在这种仇恨与悲伤的无尽连锁中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳苗跟那个男人期望你过上这样的人生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的女儿死了难道你就不伤心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我还有你 我只剩下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…您的衣物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身打扮出席的话会失礼于各位来宾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在才问晚了点 你怎么会弄成这幅样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便救了下人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢 就这样出席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了正确的事才弄脏衣物的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位对有马集团支持有加的董事以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…各位相关人员 抱歉让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫有马哲平 我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且也是有马集团总裁继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 继承人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必各位对于他这满身泥土的装束很是吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为他在来这里之前救了人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你救了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人叫夏洛特‧海瑟琳克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是海瑟琳克的公主陛下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…陛下？ 海瑟琳克公国？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的是公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位尽兴我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他这身装束对于他自己和各位来宾来说都有失礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请容他梳洗准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期间 请诸位畅谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总裁继承人是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了找到父母的仇人才来做你的养子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人会为你成为继承人一事而感到不悦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让对方明白这点 我才故意上演了刚才那幕闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗 佳苗是正统继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正统继承人？ 所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方不会马上露出马脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先要结交同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你要跟靠近你的人搞好关系 不管是不是刚才宴会上的那群小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平君跟您父亲还真是像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我也问候一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有马钢厂专务 敝姓外村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人当中…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多成年人可不应该「围观」一个孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他也感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范‧霍森卿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍森卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位想做有马先生的公子的护卫 不如去申请特别许可如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然范‧霍森卿这么吩咐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都拚命想通过你来巴结一心先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫文森特‧范‧霍森
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给介绍一下我的女儿们吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 这个哥哥就是爷爷的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能叫爷爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 她还不懂礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫玛利亚‧范‧霍森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫有马哲平 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你很拘谨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尔维呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不知去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 真拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 哲平君 今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心先生一登场 会场气氛都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好厉害的领袖气质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的身上我也感受到了相同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多也适应会场气氛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平先生 您方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪笑脸就累得我精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起你就对我很关照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女仆呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆 真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看我像什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 的确除了女仆什么都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货真价实的女仆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平先生 您要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种让人搞不清状况的时候 活动身体是最有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想和西洋剑切磋一下试试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真般配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,般配？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个哥哥和姐姐一样厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他哥哥还早了点 玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了不少事呢 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们通过剑彼此了解了对方吧？ 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是西尔维娅‧范‧霍森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平的父亲随身带着像棒子一样的怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟是做什么职业的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是：荞麦面师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集公主恋人 学园与再会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Japanese food吗 真棒


